Invocation Name: celestial white noise
des: Celestial White noise takes a space-inspired approach to promote deep sleep and focus. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Celestial White Noise,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
